  "compilation_error": "",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述自动交易系统的完整生命周期。系统启动后先进入Idle状态，然后要经过一个Gated门控检查，通过后才能进入信号检测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Idle到Gated的触发条件是什么？是时间过滤和区间门控都通过吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，条件是Session/day filters和range gate pass。Gated之后进入SignalCheck，这里要比较Close[2]和Close[1]两个收盘价。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gated",
        "SignalCheck"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，SignalCheck画好了。接下来分叉到EntryBUY和EntrySELL两个状态对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignalCheck",
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。EntryBUY的条件是Close[1]等于Close[2]且当前没有SELL持仓；EntrySELL是Close[1]小于Close[2]且没有BUY持仓。两个入场状态都要汇聚到BasketManage。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL",
        "BasketManage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "BasketManage画好了。这个状态应该可以循环加仓吧？我看到有AddMore这个状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage",
        "AddMore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AddMore的条件是价格偏离上次入场达到Step距离，并且交易次数小于MaxTrades。加仓后回到BasketManage继续管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage",
        "AddMore",
        "Step",
        "MaxTrades"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "BasketManage完成后怎么退出？需要同步止盈吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，进入SyncTP状态，这里要计算均价，然后设置止盈位为avg加减TP_pts。完成后回到Idle等待下一周期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SyncTP",
        "Idle",
        "avg",
        "TP_pts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "SyncTP到Idle画好了。不过Idle状态还需要几条退出路径吧？比如风控和平仓条件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SyncTP",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "非常重要。Idle要有三条强制平仓路径：EquityStop是浮动亏损超过TotalEquityRisk%的权益比例；HiddenTP是隐藏止盈目标达成；DailyTarget是启用日目标且当日收益达标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "EquityStop",
        "HiddenTP",
        "DailyTarget",
        "TotalEquityRisk%"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "EquityStop的条件我再确认一下：浮动盈亏小于0，且绝对值超过TotalEquityRisk% of equity，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EquityStop",
        "TotalEquityRisk%"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。这三条路径最终都要进入Flat状态清空持仓，然后Flat再回到Idle形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EquityStop",
